description.en-us: Holiday Hot Rods are a series of Exclusive Cars, in Celebration for the Holiday Seasons that started in 2006 that were sold Exclusively at Wal-Mart on single cards, below are the following years, starting with 2006. Then in 2007, Target joined in with their series the 3 pack Holiday Hot Rods as both retail stores carried the brands into 2009.
